{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/01/28/白嫖spotify的方式.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5d1dccf6-2d1a-5c7b-a3d8-7ea92212246d","excerpt":"白嫖 spotify 的方式 今年开始，我不再在家办公，这使得我的网络环境不是很稳定，无法一直在线听 spotify。最好的办法，自然是把要听的音乐缓存下来。 GitHub 里面有一个 python 项目spotify-downloader可以下载 spotify 的音频。 利用 pip…","html":"<h1>白嫖 spotify 的方式</h1>\n<p>今年开始，我不再在家办公，这使得我的网络环境不是很稳定，无法一直在线听 spotify。最好的办法，自然是把要听的音乐缓存下来。</p>\n<p>GitHub 里面有一个 python 项目<a href=\"https://github.com/ritiek/spotify-downloader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">spotify-downloader</a>可以下载 spotify 的音频。</p>\n<p>利用 pip 安装</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> spotdl</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>因为是国内使用，需要代理</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">env</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">https_proxy</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>http://127.0.0.1:1080 spotdl --song http://open.spotify.com/xxx</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>另外，spotdl 支持列表下载</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">spotdl --playlist <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>listUrl<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># to get all songs' url</span>\nspotdl --list list.txt <span class=\"token comment\"># to download the songs</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/01/28/白嫖spotify的方式.html","date":"January 28, 2020","title":"白嫖spotify的方式"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/01/28/白嫖spotify的方式.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/movie/2020/01/22/电影补档计划：告白.html","title":"电影补档计划：告白"},"frontmatter":{"category":"movie"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/01/31/monect让手机变成鼠标.html","title":"monect让手机变成鼠标"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}